1
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,940
=Ancient Bracelet=

2
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:44,380
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,660
=I Feared You Might Lose Control=

4
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:48,720
Zhaoli,

5
00:00:49,386 --> 00:00:50,583
something's wrong with Yan Che.

6
00:00:50,710 --> 00:00:51,920
You must not marry him.

7
00:00:52,710 --> 00:00:53,550
Zhaoli.

8
00:00:56,070 --> 00:00:56,910
Ying Du,

9
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,070
shame on you.

10
00:00:58,430 --> 00:00:59,710
How could you drug me?

11
00:01:01,860 --> 00:01:04,420
(Everlasting Joy)

12
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,120
Your Highness,

13
00:01:06,310 --> 00:01:07,840
the ruler brought back a young woman.

14
00:01:08,310 --> 00:01:09,170
From the sound of it,

15
00:01:09,230 --> 00:01:10,870
they share a very close bond.

16
00:01:12,590 --> 00:01:13,430
Find out

17
00:01:15,310 --> 00:01:16,150
who she is.

18
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:17,350
Yes.

19
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:26,700
(Everlasting Joy)

20
00:01:30,150 --> 00:01:32,400
Did you rest well last night?

21
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,150
I haven't slept all night,

22
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,510
and I'm very exhausted.

23
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:37,070
Finish what you came to say.

24
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,920
I'll need a bit of rest after.

25
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,120
Your Majesty,

26
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,590
don't push your luck.

27
00:01:53,790 --> 00:01:54,630
Stop pretending.

28
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,790
Do it.

29
00:01:56,150 --> 00:01:57,710
If you mean to take my life,

30
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,590
why humiliate me like this?

31
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:01,840
(Yan Che's true identity)

32
00:02:01,859 --> 00:02:04,113
(and his purpose for approaching
Zhaoli remain unknown.)

33
00:02:04,150 --> 00:02:05,790
(It's not yet time to deal with him.)

34
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,000
Your Majesty,

35
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:10,000
please return my wife to me.

36
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,630
You dare demand someone from me?

37
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:13,630
You've got quite the courage.

38
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:15,190
For Zhaoli,

39
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,120
I'd willingly face death.

40
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,150
You use sweet words like these

41
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,870
to deceive Zhaoli, right?

42
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:30,430
You'd better

43
00:02:31,150 --> 00:02:33,280
keep up this act
for the rest of your life.

44
00:03:00,840 --> 00:03:02,150
Why look at me like that?

45
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:05,150
You know very well

46
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,840
what you've done to me.

47
00:03:08,740 --> 00:03:09,640
You heartless creature.

48
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,470
What did I do to you?

49
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:14,000
You should ask what you did to me.

50
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:17,280
How could you drug me?

51
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,360
If I desired you,

52
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:21,280
I'd never stoop to such means.

53
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:22,400
It's so hot.

54
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,240
I feel awful.

55
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,080
Zhaoli,

56
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:26,920
what are you doing?

57
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,960
Zhaoli,

58
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:40,590
you've been poisoned.

59
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,960
We must purge the poison at once.

60
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:52,600
Don't move.

61
00:03:52,630 --> 00:03:53,710
Let me cleanse the poison.

62
00:03:59,910 --> 00:04:00,750
Zhaoli,

63
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,310
calm yourself.

64
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,710
That's the truth of what happened.

65
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:10,080
You were poisoned.

66
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:11,840
Everything you saw was just an illusion.

67
00:04:12,166 --> 00:04:13,360
But if you insist on believing

68
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,750
that I've done something to you,

69
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:15,990
so be it.

70
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,480
Then why have you tied me up?

71
00:04:20,872 --> 00:04:22,099
I feared you might lose control

72
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,080
toward me.

73
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:26,480
You're pretending to be all noble now?

74
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,480
Since you claim to be so righteous,

75
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,720
why did you drag me here by force?

76
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:37,750
I want you to marry me.

77
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,510
Keep dreaming.

78
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,360
At this point,

79
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:43,750
whether you wish it or not,

80
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:45,430
you will be.

81
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,920
This wedding robe was made just for you.

82
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:51,350
Try it on.

83
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,430
I'll never wear it.

84
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,430
Then you don't have to.

85
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,560
I'll simply announce it to the world.

86
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,190
What exactly are you planning?

87
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,510
Whatever Yan Che can give you,

88
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,430
I will give you far more.

89
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,800
I won't let you suffer any grievance.

90
00:05:13,870 --> 00:05:14,710
Your Highness,

91
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:15,720
I know I was wrong.

92
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:17,120
You drugged her?

93
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,950
I didn't want Che

94
00:05:25,390 --> 00:05:27,120
to marry her.

95
00:05:27,321 --> 00:05:28,425
But I never imagined the one

96
00:05:28,436 --> 00:05:30,686
who spent that night with her
would be the ruler.

97
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,110
Your Highness,

98
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,720
please, help me.

99
00:05:34,750 --> 00:05:35,600
Do not worry.

100
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,430
I will protect you.

101
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,630
So, you know who that woman is.

102
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:42,360
She's just a humble healer
from our Wuyue tribe.

103
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,830
Since you know her so well,

104
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:49,070
do something for me.

105
00:05:49,296 --> 00:05:51,000
(Everlasting Joy)
This is a family banquet.

106
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,950
Members of the Wuyue tribe,
please feel at ease.

107
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:53,800
A family banquet?

108
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,070
But we share

109
00:05:55,070 --> 00:05:56,630
no marriage ties with the ruler.

110
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:59,240
Does he seek alliance through marriage?

111
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,600
Ying Du, have you caused enough trouble?

112
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:02,910
Trouble?

113
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:05,070
I never waste time on trifles.

114
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:07,350
Here, open your mouth.

115
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,960
Not going to eat?

116
00:06:11,870 --> 00:06:13,680
Shall I give it
to your grandmother instead?

117
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,960
Don't rush.

118
00:06:27,343 --> 00:06:28,270
If you're still hungry,

119
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:29,920
I'll feed you more in the bedchamber.

120
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,120
You've never shown interest in women.

121
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:34,950
I wonder which young lady

122
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,440
is worthy to stand by your side.

123
00:06:37,430 --> 00:06:38,870
The one beside me

124
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,830
is naturally my wife.

125
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:43,590
Your wife?

126
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,560
You're not married.

127
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:46,700
Nor do you keep any consorts.

128
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,240
Who exactly is she?

129
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,090
What now?

130
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,240
Must I report it to you

131
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,000
before I get married?

132
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,190
I am merely curious.

133
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,920
Besides, by doing so,

134
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,920
you're breaking the rules.

135
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,780
So what?

136
00:07:00,780 --> 00:07:01,660
Indeed.

137
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,120
It is against protocol.

138
00:07:03,232 --> 00:07:04,569
Have you caused enough of a scene?

139
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,390
How long do you intend to disgrace me?

140
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,830
Please reveal

141
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:12,750
her identity.

142
00:07:14,190 --> 00:07:15,360
Let go of me!

143
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,480
(Why hasn't the wound)

144
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,070
(healed yet?)

145
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:23,630
It seems

146
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,190
she hasn't grown used to her title.

147
00:07:25,533 --> 00:07:26,440
Since that's the case,

148
00:07:26,473 --> 00:07:28,040
there's no need for you all to meet her.

149
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,240
All you need to know today

150
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,310
is that I've taken a wife.

151
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:36,960
Your Majesty,

152
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:38,750
why bother hiding it?

153
00:07:39,270 --> 00:07:40,830
Others may not see it clearly,

154
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,750
but I can see it plain as day.

155
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,040
Your wife

156
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,630
is just Zhaoli.

157
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,480
Zhaoli?

158
00:07:46,510 --> 00:07:48,083
Didn't she marry the future chief?

159
00:07:48,094 --> 00:07:49,310
How could she marry the ruler?

160
00:07:49,310 --> 00:07:51,160
- That's right!
- Is she really Zhaoli?

161
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,623
What's going on here?

162
00:07:52,755 --> 00:07:53,856
Zhaoli and the future chief

163
00:07:53,867 --> 00:07:55,265
have been betrothed since childhood.

164
00:07:55,276 --> 00:07:56,630
Why would she approach the ruler?

165
00:07:56,630 --> 00:07:58,430
She's chasing wealth and status.

166
00:07:58,560 --> 00:08:00,070
Does she not see her own place?

167
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:01,310
You are Wu Luoluo?

168
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,450
Yes.

169
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,766
Slandering my wife without reason

170
00:08:03,853 --> 00:08:05,040
is treated as a grave offense.

171
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:07,480
Guards, take her away to the dungeon.

172
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,480
- Yes.
- Your Majesty,

173
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,750
what did I say that was wrong?

174
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,183
Wu Zhaoli is unfaithful.

175
00:08:11,194 --> 00:08:12,510
She's unworthy of being your wife.

176
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:13,350
Move.

177
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,960
Let me go!

178
00:08:16,950 --> 00:08:18,070
If it truly is Zhaoli,

179
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,750
please stop making mistakes.

180
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,640
Yan Che,

181
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:23,310
if you don't dare to show

182
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:25,160
those thoughts in your heart,

183
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:27,040
don't use Zhaoli as your excuse.

184
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:29,680
Before you stand against me,

185
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,200
think carefully of your father

186
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,510
and your people first.

187
00:08:34,670 --> 00:08:35,530
Che,

188
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:37,150
this matter ends here.

189
00:08:37,316 --> 00:08:38,850
Do not bring ruin upon the whole tribe.

190
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,870
- But...
- There is no but.

191
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,720
Between the tribe and Wu Zhaoli,

192
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,800
you must make

193
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:48,320
a choice today.

194
00:08:53,370 --> 00:08:58,020
♪Snow falls upon my brows,
blurring suddenly♪

195
00:08:59,850 --> 00:09:04,820
♪Memories turn,
forgiving time after time♪

196
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:09,560
♪Tears or snowflakes, sweet or bitter♪

197
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:12,460
♪Hard to tell them apart♪

198
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:18,270
♪Vowing to give you
three lifetimes' happiness♪

199
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:21,970
♪In this life, I still run toward you♪

200
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:24,670
♪No matter the homeward journey♪

201
00:09:24,670 --> 00:09:28,710
♪Falling to the deepest place
in your heart♪

202
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:31,090
♪And that is enough♪

203
00:09:31,090 --> 00:09:34,880
♪Ahead lies a path without snow or wind♪

204
00:09:35,090 --> 00:09:37,850
♪Begonia blooms across the branches♪

205
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:43,970
♪One more glance
may let love stand still♪

